===============
Version 2.25.91
===============

  Panel

	* Remove the mixer applet from the default configuration since MATE
	  upstream doesn't ship this applet by default. Some distributions
	  might want to put it back. The patch to be reverted is:
	  http://svn.mate.org/viewvc/mate-panel/trunk/mate-panel/panel-default-setup.entries?r1=11171&r2=11512&view=patch
	  (Vincent)

  Clock Applet

	* Fix properties dialog to not have a missing image and a weird title
	  (Matthias Clasen)
	* Use new GTK+ feature to change orientation of GtkBox instead of
	  custom code (Christian Persch)

  Notification Area Applet

	* Use new GTK+ feature to change orientation of GtkBox instead of
	  custom code (Christian Persch)

  Misc

	* Require GTK+ 2.15.1 (Christian Persch)

  Docs Translators

	* Iñaki Larrañaga Murgoitio (eu)

  Translators

	* Astur (ast)
	* Ihar Hrachyshka (be@latin)
	* Alexander Shopov (bg)
	* Ask Hjorth Larsen (da)
	* Dawa pemo (dz)
	* Jorge González (es)
