	* Ensure locations show the local time (Matthias Clasen)
	* Also fix the problem where the time is invisible for
	  a while after the popup has been shown (Matthias Clasen)
	* Fix the display of the weather on the panel (Matthias Clasen)
	* Take daylight savings time into account for local times (Matthias Clasen)
	* Fix complication when polkit is not available (Frederic Peters)

