Version 2.21.5
==============

  Misc

	* New dependencies for the clock applet: rsvg, d-bus, polkit,
	  NetworkManager. NetworkManager is optional, polkit might not be
	  optional yet but should be in the near future

  Clock Applet

	* Merge intlclock with the clock applet (lots of people, but the merge
	  was mainly done by Federico Mena Quintero and Matthias Clasen)

  Window List Applet

	* HIG fixes (Christian Persch)

