==============
Version 2.19.2
==============

  Panel

	* Code cleanups (Vincent)
	* Force the panel to not be restarted when there's already a panel
	  running, fix endless loop of error dialogs (Vincent)
	* Add a checkbox to let the user choose to not restart the panel if
	  there was a problem registering with matecomponent at startup (Vincent)
	* Default the "Applet disappeared" dialog to reload (Vincent)
	* Default the "Can't load applet" dialog to not delete (Vincent)
	* Small HIG improvements to the launcher editor (Vincent)
	* Fix alignment of the run label in the run dialog (Vincent)
	* Fix creation of launchers with empty spaces in the command (Vincent)
	* Fix the launcher editor to not save a full-path icon for the
	  non-localized icon when it's not needed (Vincent)
	* Fix mate-desktop-item-edit work for relative URI when creating a
	  .directory file (Vincent)
	* Use the launcher icon as a fallback for launchers without an icon
	  (Vincent)
	* Guess the icon when the user enters a command in the launcher editor
	  (Vincent)
	* Use macros for name icons to easily change the name of named icons
	  when needed (Vincent)
	* Check whether reboot is enabled in gdm (and not only shutdown) and
	  only show the buttons when they're useful in the logout dialog
	  (Brian Cameron)
	* Prefer /var/run/gdm_socket as path for the GDM socket (Loïc Minier)
	* Take into account NAME_MAX for the length of the filename when
	  guessing a name for launchers in mate-desktop-item-edit (Vincent)
	* Fix creation of launcher when dragging an URL with ? or : (Vincent)
	* Make some error dialogs visible in the taskbar and make some other
	  transient to the panel (Vincent)

  Clock Applet

	* Don't display tasks that are marked completed (Ross Burton)
	* Update the clock when the configuration tool exits so that the user
	  doesn't have to wait up to one minute to see the change (Ray Strode)
	* Fix preferences window to not hide the custom format when it should
	  be shown (Jamie Fox)
	* Document that the custom format is the format used by strftime
	  (Vincent)
	* Show the date by default in the applet (Vincent)
	* Let distributor easily specify their configuation tool instead of
	  hardcoding everything (Vincent)
	* Update the clock every second for UNIX format (Vincent)
	* Make Internet time work a bit better (Vincent)

  Notification Area Applet

	* Fix compiler warning (Vincent)

  Misc

	* Install data files in $(datadir)/mate-panel/ instead of
	  $(datadir)/mate/panel/ (Vincent)
	* Add --with-clock-time-utility configure flag
	* Run gtk-update-icon-cache on uninstall
	* Make .desktop file used for bug-buddy translatable

  Docs

	* Migrate documentation for window list and workspace switcher to the
	  user guide (Karderio, Vincent)

  Docs Translators

	* Jorge Gonzalez (es)
	* Changwoo Ryu (ko)

  Translators

	* Ihar Hrachyshka (be@latin)
	* Vladimir Petkov (bg)
	* Jordi Mallach (ca)
