===============
Version 2.17.92
===============

  Panel

	* Fix wrong initial position of menu (Vincent)
	* Code cleanups (Vincent)
	* Add missing mnemonics in main menu (Padraig O'Briain, Vincent)
	* Don't show multiple times a dialog about an applet failing to load
	  (Vincent)
	* Don't try to load again in the same session an applet that failed to
	  load before (Vincent)
	* Get localized names when starting a launcher so that the startup
	  notification use the translated name (Vincent)
	* Fix image size on the run dialog so that it's always the correct size
	  (Vincent)
	* Set automatic gravity for the labels in the menubar, so that japanese
	  and other scripts are correctly displayed on vertical panels
	  (Behdad Esfahbod, Vincent)

  Workspace Switcher Applet

	* Make mouse scrolling correctly work in RTL environments (Vincent)
	* Performance improvement when a workspace is renamed/added/removed.
	  This has an important impact when accessibility is turned on.
	  (Vincent)
	* Fix speed of the spin button for number of workspaces (Vincent)

  Clock Applet

	* Set automatic gravity for the clock label, so that japanese and other
	  scripts are correctly displayed on vertical panels (Vincent)
	* Make it possible to use markup for the clock text, which is useful
	  with custom format (Vincent)
	* Don't wake up every second if it's not necessary (Matthias Clasen,
	  Vincent)

  Misc

	* Add missing check for mateconf for libmate-panel-applet (Vincent)
	* Require pango 1.15.4 (Vincent)
	* Distribute MAINTAINERS (Kjartan Maraas)

  Docs

	* Update fish screenshot (Luca Ferretti)

