===============
Version 2.17.91
===============

  Panel

	* Make the main menu usable with a11y tools (Padraig O'Briain)
	* Revert changes related to settings menu (Vincent)
	* Fix crash when saving a new Link launcher (Vincent)
	* Improve a lot the panel in RTL environments (yair)

  Misc

	* Optional check for libedataserver for the clock (Brian Cameron)

  Docs Translators

	* APS Alam (pa)
	* Daniel Nylander (sv)

  Translators

	* Khaled Hosny (ar)
