===============
Version 2.17.90
===============

  Panel

	* Remove code warning (JP Rosevear)
	* Change text of some menu items (Luca Ferretti)
	* Use GTK_STOCK_MISSING_IMAGE when the icon of a launcher can't be
	  found and remove useless error dialog (Thomas Wood)
	* Use better filenames when creating launchers (Dan Winship, Vincent)
	* Simplify system menu code thanks to new control center shell
	  (Vincent)
	* Fix "Add to panel" dialog to correctly display capplets (Vincent)
	* Migrate settings menu buttons to a control center shell launcher
	  (Vincent)
	* Use 22 as default icon sizes for menus (Vincent)
	* Force size of launchers to 16, 22, 32 or 48 (Vincent)
	* Use new launcher icon (Vincent)
	* Fix compilation on darwin (Vincent)
	* Fix disappearing launcher on drag and drop (and other related issues)
	  (Vincent)
	* Fix transparency broken when screen size changes (bugreports@nn7.de)
	* Don't accept every command line option, but only the deprecated
	  --profile (Vincent)
	* Check for the logout_prompt mateconf key to know whether we should show
	  the logout dialog or just log out (Ray Strode, Vincent)
	* Do not start dragging an applet when it's not possible because a grab
	  is active, fix change of cursor icon in this case (Amnon Aaronsohn)
	* Do not hardcode invisible_char in glade files (Vitaliy Ischenko)
	* Correctly position applet menu in RTL environments (Vincent)
	* Really remove launcher file when deleting a launcher, and do it only
	  when possible (Vincent)
	* Fix main menu not completely reloading when the menu is updated
	  (Vincent)

  mate-desktop-item-edit

	* Make it possible to create a .directory file with a name instead of
	  forcing the name to $(dir)/.directory (Vincent)
	* Use new launcher icon (Vincent)
	* Make --create-new usage more logical (Vincent)

  libmate-panel-applet

	* Do not hardcode invisible_char in glade files (Vitaliy Ischenko)
	* Correctly position applet menu in RTL environments (Vincent)

  Clock Applet

	* Look for evolution binary before trying to run it (Vincent)
	* Make sure that the last day of a multi-day events is marked in the
	  calendar Michael Frank)
	* Don't mark multiple days on the calendar if the event is an all day
	  event (Vincent)
	* Fix compilation on some systems (Vincent)
	* Launch evolution when double-clicking on a task (Nickolay V. Shmyrev,
	  Vincent)

  Fish Applet

	* HIG fix (Vincent)
	* Do not hardcode invisible_char in glade files (Vitaliy Ischenko)

  Notification Area Applet

	* Add a test-tray program (Christian Persch)

  Workspace Switcher Applet

	* Slow down speed of the spin button for number of workspaces
	  (Manu Cornet)

  Misc

	* New launcher icon
	* Build fixes (Vincent)

  Documentation

	* Add a link to the user guide (Claude Paroz)

  Docs Translators

	* Nickolay V. Shmyrev (ru)

  Translators

	* Khaled Hosny (ar)
	* Ihar Hrachyshka (be)
