	* Fix major X leak with translucent panels (Kristian Rietveld)
	* Use a new "applications" icon for the applications menu (Glynn, Jakub Steiner)
	* Set accessible names for drawers and hide buttons (Padraig)
	* Fix issue with "Log Out blah" menu item and username's with underscore (Jordy Potman)
	* Remove bogus panel_signal_connect_object_while_alive() (Mark)
	* Fix issue where "Delete this Panel" wasn't visible (Jason Leach)
	* Only allow resizing the run dialog if the proram list is visible (Leena Gunda)
	* Fix some runtime warnings (Mark)
	* Fix some portability issues (The Written Word)

  libmate-panel-applet

	* Install enums header and fix signal definitions (Bryan Forbes, Mark)
	* Build panel-test-applets with -export-dynamic (Vincent Berger)

  Clock Applet

	* Fix bug where selected calendars were out of sync (Jon McCann)
	* Use UTC time for events if preference set (Jon)
	* Correctly detect all day events (Jon)
	* Re-position the calendar popup as the clock is moved around (Jon)
	* Don't show "Adjust Date & Time" if no config tool available (Fernando Herrera)
	* Fix issue with ellipsizing the task description (Mark)

  Misc

	* Sync with newer version of the recent files implementation (Mark)
	* Use a themed window icon in the screenshooter (Fernando Herrera)
	* Fix issue with unsetting the preferred command for Wanda (Maneesh Pusalkar)
	* Set the accessible name on the notification area (Padraig)
	* Fix underquoted definition of AM_PATH_ESD (Alexander Winston)
	* Fix invalid UTF8 in spanish help docs (John Fleck)
	* Bump required GTK+ to 2.3.2 (Jason Leach)

  Translators

