	* Add hidden accelerators to the Main Menu and Applications menu (Mark, George)
	* Fix moving of drawers from one panel to another (George)
	* Support partial width struts to considerably improve desktop
	  usability with Xinerama (Rob Adams, Mark)
	* Change the default icon size in menus to 24x24 (Mark)
	* Re-work error dialog generation to make localisation easier (Christian Neumair)
