  o Translators

	* Abel Cheung (zh_TW.po), Andrew W. Nosenko (ru.po), Christian Rose (sv.po),
	  Dafydd Harries (cy.po), Dinesh Nadarajah (ta.po), Hasbullah Bin Pit (ms.po),
	  Jordi Mallach (ca.po), Kostas Papadimas (el.po), Miloslav Trmac (cs.po),
	  Reinout van Schouwen (nl.po), Takayuki KUSANO (ja.po),
	  Vincent van Adrighem (li.po) and Wang Li (zh_CN.po).

===============
Version 2.3.2.1
===============

  o Panel

	* Implement the ability to lock individual applets to the panel (Mark)
	* Popup either the Applications Menu or Main Menu with Alt-F1 (Mark)
	* When adding a new object, don't move other objects out of the way (Mark)
	* Fix weirdness with creating new panels just after deleting ones (Ray Strode)
	* Fix panel properties dialog crashes with duff MateConf settings (Ray)
	* Don't include copy of mate-vfs function in new run dialog (Mark)
	* Fix crash after moving applets between panels (Arvind)
	* HIGify new run dialog (Dennis Cranston)
	* Fix silly 64bit problem with setting the panel struts (Mark)
	* Save screenshots in ~/Desktop not ~/.mate-desktop (Mark)
	* Fix problem with re-parenting Main Menu buttons (Mark)
	* Fix incorrect initial position when adding launchers (Mark)
	* Remove heaps of unused code (Mark)

  o Applets

	* Close the about dialog when the applet is removed (Leena Gunda)

  o Misc

	* Fix some warnings (Ray)
	* Fix numerous typos (Christian Rose, Ray)

  o Translations

	* Abel Cheung (fa, bn), Christian Rose (sv), Duarte Loreto (pt)
	  and Miloslav Trmac (cs).

