Version 2.3.2
=============

  o Panel

	* Re-write of the run dialog (Frank Worsley)
	* Add "Force Quit" action button (Mark)
	* Add support for re-sizing during panel animations (Mark)
	* Fix many bugs with the new drawer implementation (Mark)
	* Re-implement launcher hoarding (Mark)
	* Don't save absolute paths in MateConf (Mark)
	* Load panel defaults using mateconftool --load (Mark)
	* Fix some of the more major issues with migrating to 2.3 (Mark)
	* Fix problems with menu hierarchy as reported to a11y (Padraig)
	* Convert filename to UTF8 before displaying (Toshi)
	* Fix jitteriness in the run dialog (nix AT go-nix.ca)
	* Make alert windows use OK, not CLOSE (Greg Merchan)
	* Typo fixes (Miloslav Trmac, Duarte Loreto)

  o Applets

	* Much HIG compliance work (Dennis Cranston)
	* Destroy about dialogs when applets are removed (Bala)

  o libmate-panel-applet

	* Completely document all libmate-panel-applet functions (Mark)
	* Implement mate_panel_applet_mateconf_(set|get)_list (Mark)
	* Remove C99ism from an enum declaration (Mark)
	* Fix bug with recursing when associating schemas (Yatin Chawathe)

  o Misc

	* Fix sgmldocs.make (Art Haas)
	* Cygwin fixes (Masahiro Sakai)
