Version 2.2.1
=============

Panel

	* Make global keybindings work on multi-screen setups (Erwann, Mark)
	* Destroy "Create Launcher" dialogs when the panel is destrored (Arvind)
	* Allow the MATE foot icon on the Main Menu to be themed (Raj)
	* Support themeing of the action button icons (Raj)
	* Query deletion of a drawer when it is deleted by removing the button (Arvind)
	* Delete child drawer panels when deleting panels (Arvind)
	* Fix various leaks (Kjartan)
	* Fix typo with the launchers "zoom animation" (Paul Gammans)
	* Do not query the deletion of a panel if there are no objects on it (Heeten, Arvind)
	* Make the "Delete Panel?" dialog modal (Arvind)
	* Avoid rare panel hang when moving applets (Sunil Mohan Adapa)
	* Actually load the panel background color preference (Greg Hudson)
	* Fix crash related to drawers (Arvind)
	* Fix various issues with egg-recent-files (James)
	* Don't save screenshot to UTF8 filenames in G_BROKEN_FILENAMES locales (Toshi)
	* Fix crash when the panel background image can't be loaded (Mark, Heeten)
	* Unescape the tooltip on launchers (Bala)
	* Destroy the "Overwrite file?" warning dialog in mate-panel-screenshot (Bala)
	* Add support for icon theming icons with absolute paths (Mark, Havoc, Raj)
	* Don't crash when clicking on a drawer panel with no parent panel (Mark)
	* Don't load the MATE 1.4 applet's .desktop files on startup (Mark)

