	* Changwoo Ryu, Christian Meyer, Christian Rose, Christophe Merlet,
	  Dmitry G. Mastrukov, Frederic Crozat, Hasbullah Bin Pit, Jordi Mallach,
	  Kjartan Maraas,  Ole Laursen, Pablo Saratxaga, Pauli Virtanen and
	  Zbigniew Chyla.

=============
Version 2.0.2
=============

Panel

	* Duplicate function removal (Frederic Crozat)
	* Remove MATE_PANEL_DESKTOP_AREA root window hint (Mark)
	* Cleanups and bugfixes mulitscreen support implementation (Mark)
	* Fix crash in run dialog disclosure animation (Mark)
	* Sanity check matecomponent-activation return values (Mark)
	* String changes and UI consistency changes (Glynn, Mark)
	* Load icons for run dialog in idle instead of timeout (Jonathon)
	* Pop up the global menu on panel keybinding (Glynn)
	* .desktop file encoding fixes (George, Toshi)
	* Use X-MATE-DocPath instead of DocPath (Glynn, Mark)
	* Check mateconf string returns (Havoc, Mark)
	* Use fallback values when convert strings to enums (Mark)
	* Save launchers to disk in idle handler (Mark)
	* Better error handling in button creation (Mark, George)
	* Better error handling loading .desktop files (Havoc)
	* Fix default launchers URIs (Mark)

Fish Applet

	* Use root window instead of offscreen popup when creating pixmaps (Mark)
	* Sanity check some preferences (Mark)
	* Convert fortune output from user locale to UTF-8 (Miguel Rodríguez Pérez)
	* Warn the user if we can't locate or execute fortune (Mark)

