	* Big clean up of mate-panel-preferances (Mark)
	* Rename .glade2 files to .glade (Mark)
	* Compile warnings fixes (Mark)
	* Check for scrollkeeper at configure time (Ali Akcaagac)
	* Use private umask and remove temp dir in mate-panel-screenshot (Rohit R)

